column4: Our destination is within walking distance of the town centre, national museum and many attractions in Livingstone. It is a mere 10 minutes' drive to the Airport and the mighty VICTORIA FALLS. Our guests find the swimming to be irresistible, and the staff is amazing. Our guest house boasts eight ensuite rooms all fitted with air-conditioning units and mosquito nets. Free Internet is accessible from all our rooms.

Our Villa is a 5 bedroom, 6 bathroom piece of Paradise guaranteed to satisfy everyone in your clan! The setting is the beautiful Zambian bush - each day will greet you with visions of wandering impala, sable, bushbuck, zebra, puku, hartebeest and myriad exotic birds. Walk or bike the 10km of trails. Return to the Villa and plunge into the pool or relax with a cool drink.

The Exotic Waterall Lodge is a very luxurious and stylish private house in Zambia's Livingstone that was designed to accommodate families and groups of up to eight people. This self-catering rental has its own pool, and it is a great base for an exclusive safari holiday.
